CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. 26 reads: "Who Will Be "Miss WILY"? you pick the winner...Marjorie Parker, Pittsburgh, Announcement of the winner and the coronation of "Miss WILY" will take place at Warners Cinerama, 336 Fifth Ave., Tuesday Evening, November 27th."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Marjorie Parker wearing blouse and striped jumper, posed in interior with light colored walls for "Miss WILY" contest
